title: Detroit Pastor Fatally Shoots Brick-Wielding Man During Afternoon Service
text:
Detroit Pastor Fatally Shoots Brick-Wielding Man During Afternoon Service 
Published By: Gawker.com - Yesterday 
The pastor of a Detroit storefront church fatally shot a man who was threatening him with a brick during an afternoon service today, reports...
